level_rune_05-01.name: Windswept Highland
level_rune_05-01.description: These perennially windswept highlands, far away from the paths of any nomadic cities, are believed to harbor hostile enemy forces. Investigate the situation and repel the threat.

enemy_dlancer_2.description: All [Sarkaz Lancers] Max HP +80%, speed-based dash damage becomes 1000%, dash acceleration is now 1.5x
